% ====================================================================
% test_bestagon_proto_capture.trx -- run examples/bestagon-proto/
% proto-capture.trx via the tests/ harness.
% ====================================================================
%
% Thin wrapper: loads proto-capture.trx (Phase 0.6H: capture state
% machine per GDD section 10).
%
% 22 assertions across 7 fixture sections:
%   A: single Inf captures neutral city in 2 turns (HP10 + 10 = 20)
%   B: Inf moves off mid-capture -> progress + capturer reset
%   C: Inf wounded to HP 4 mid-capture -> 4 ticks total (slowed)
%   D: HQ capture -> previous owner faction.state = /defeated
%   E: Boots /capture-speed-pct = 50 (floor[hp*1.5]) -- HP5 caps in 3 ticks
%   F: Boots Super /auto-start-captures -- Inf on enemy city auto-begins
%   G: save/restore atomicity -- mutation visible inside bracket, reverted
%
% Throws on any assertion mismatch.  Runs on default 1 MB VM in << 1 s.
% ====================================================================

(examples/bestagon-proto/proto-capture.trx) run
(__test_ok__) =
